            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>minced beef</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
